<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Agentic ERP — Data Architecture Mapping</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0A0A0E;
    --surface: #121218;
    --surface-2: #1A1A22;
    --surface-3: #22222C;
    --border: #2A2A36;
    --border-light: #3A3A48;
    --text: #E8E6E3;
    --text-secondary: #9A9AA8;
    --text-muted: #6A6A78;

    /* Medallion */
    --bronze: #CD7F32;
    --bronze-bg: rgba(205,127,50,0.08);
    --bronze-border: rgba(205,127,50,0.28);
    --silver: #B8B9BD;
    --silver-bg: rgba(184,185,189,0.08);
    --silver-border: rgba(184,185,189,0.28);
    --gold: #D4AF37;
    --gold-bg: rgba(212,175,55,0.08);
    --gold-border: rgba(212,175,55,0.28);

    /* Accents */
    --accent: #4ECDC4;
    --accent-bg: rgba(78,205,196,0.08);
    --accent-border: rgba(78,205,196,0.28);
    --red: #FF6B6B;
    --red-bg: rgba(255,107,107,0.06);
    --purple: #A78BFA;
    --purple-bg: rgba(167,139,250,0.08);
    --green: #6BCB77;
    --green-bg: rgba(107,203,119,0.08);

    /* Platform brands */
    --snowflake: #29B5E8;
    --snowflake-bg: rgba(41,181,232,0.08);
    --snowflake-border: rgba(41,181,232,0.28);
    --databricks: #FF3621;
    --databricks-bg: rgba(255,54,33,0.08);
    --databricks-border: rgba(255,54,33,0.28);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 80% -10%, rgba(78,205,196,0.05), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(900px 500px at -10% 110%, rgba(167,139,250,0.04), transparent 60%);
  }

  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.4'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.03;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 32px 120px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 56px;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }
  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .hero-meta .dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent);
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 68px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .hero .lede {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 780px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .hero .lede strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  .section {
    padding: 72px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── MEDALLION LAYERS ── */
  .medallion-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .layer {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 3px solid;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .layer:hover { transform: translateX(4px); }
  .layer.bronze { border-left-color: var(--bronze); }
  .layer.silver { border-left-color: var(--silver); }
  .layer.gold { border-left-color: var(--gold); }
  .layer-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .layer-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .layer.bronze .layer-title { color: var(--bronze); }
  .layer.silver .layer-title { color: var(--silver); }
  .layer.gold .layer-title { color: var(--gold); }
  .layer-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1px solid;
  }
  .layer.bronze .layer-tag { color: var(--bronze); border-color: var(--bronze-border); background: var(--bronze-bg); }
  .layer.silver .layer-tag { color: var(--silver); border-color: var(--silver-border); background: var(--silver-bg); }
  .layer.gold .layer-tag { color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold-border); background: var(--gold-bg); }
  .layer-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .agents-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .agent {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .agent .marker {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .agent.llm .marker { background: var(--purple); }
  .agent.det .marker { background: var(--accent); }
  .agent.ml .marker { background: var(--gold); }
  .agent.human .marker { background: var(--red); }
  .agent .name { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .agent .type { color: var(--text-muted); }

  .legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .legend-item .marker { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }

  /* ── DATA VAULT ── */
  .vault-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .vault-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .vault-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 32px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }
  .vault-type {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .vault-card h3 {
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .vault-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .vault-examples {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
    padding-top: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .vault-examples strong { color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── DATA MESH ── */
  .mesh-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mesh-cell {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 28px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .mesh-cell:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .mesh-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  .mesh-cell h4 {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .mesh-cell p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── HOW IT WORKS (Q&A) ── */
  .qa-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .qa {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
  }
  .qa-q {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .qa-a {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .qa-a strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .qa-a code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ── DEPLOYMENT VIEWS (NEW) ── */
  .deploy-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid;
  }
  .deploy-header.snowflake { border-color: var(--snowflake-border); }
  .deploy-header.databricks { border-color: var(--databricks-border); }
  .deploy-logo {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .deploy-header.snowflake .deploy-logo {
    background: var(--snowflake-bg);
    color: var(--snowflake);
    border: 1px solid var(--snowflake-border);
  }
  .deploy-header.databricks .deploy-logo {
    background: var(--databricks-bg);
    color: var(--databricks);
    border: 1px solid var(--databricks-border);
  }
  .deploy-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .deploy-header.snowflake .deploy-title { color: var(--snowflake); }
  .deploy-header.databricks .deploy-title { color: var(--databricks); }
  .deploy-sub {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .deploy-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .deploy-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .deploy-row.snowflake { border-left: 3px solid var(--snowflake); }
  .deploy-row.databricks { border-left: 3px solid var(--databricks); }
  .deploy-cell-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  .deploy-cell-component {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .deploy-cell-component span {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-top: 4px;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .deploy-row.snowflake .deploy-cell-component { color: var(--snowflake); }
  .deploy-row.databricks .deploy-cell-component { color: var(--databricks); }
  .deploy-cell-detail {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .deploy-callout {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .deploy-callout.snowflake { border-color: var(--snowflake-border); }
  .deploy-callout.databricks { border-color: var(--databricks-border); }
  .deploy-callout strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .deploy-callout.snowflake strong { color: var(--snowflake); }
  .deploy-callout.databricks strong { color: var(--databricks); }

  /* ── DEFENCE LAYERS ── */
  .defence-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .defence-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--red);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .defence-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--red);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .defence-card h4 {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .defence-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── ROSETTA TABLE ── */
  .comp-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 8px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .comp-table th,
  .comp-table td {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .comp-table th {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: var(--surface-2);
  }
  .comp-table td {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .comp-table td:first-child {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .comp-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .comp-table tr:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
  .moat-row td:nth-child(2),
  .moat-row td:nth-child(3) {
    color: var(--red);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .moat-callout {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .moat-callout strong { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    margin-top: 80px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 2;
  }
  .footer em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container { padding: 40px 20px 80px; }
    .deploy-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .deploy-cell-label { margin-bottom: -8px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      <span>Architecture Reference · v2</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>Snowflake & Databricks Deployment Views Added</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Agentic ERP — mapped to <em>Medallion</em>, <em>Data Vault</em>, and <em>Data Mesh</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Same architecture, two vocabularies. This document re-expresses the agentic fund administration platform
      in the language used by Snowflake and Databricks practitioners — and shows what the deployment topology
      actually looks like on each platform. The goal is <strong>shared language for industry conversations</strong>
      without diluting what makes the architecture distinctive: deterministic verification of probabilistic outputs.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- ═══ SECTION 1: MEDALLION LAYER MAPPING ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
    <div class="section-label">Section 01</div>
    <h2>Medallion Layer Mapping</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">
      The nine agents in the platform map cleanly to Bronze / Silver / Gold. The interesting part is the
      <strong style="color:var(--text)">mix of agent types within each layer</strong> — LLM, deterministic,
      ML, and human-in-the-loop — which is what differentiates an agentic ERP from a standard pipeline.
    </p>

    <div class="medallion-grid">

      <div class="layer bronze">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <div class="layer-title">Bronze · Raw Capture</div>
          <span class="layer-tag">Land · Extract · Classify</span>
        </div>
        <p class="layer-desc">
          Documents arrive in any format. The Bronze tier classifies and extracts — no business logic applied,
          no calculations performed. Confidence scores flow downstream. This is where probabilistic AI is most
          valuable and most contained.
        </p>
        <div class="agents-row">
          <div class="agent llm"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A1 · Intake</span><span class="type">LLM (Haiku)</span></div>
          <div class="agent llm"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A2 · Reader</span><span class="type">LLM (Sonnet/Haiku)</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="layer silver">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <div class="layer-title">Silver · Verified Calculation</div>
          <span class="layer-tag">Generate · Validate · Verify</span>
        </div>
        <p class="layer-desc">
          The Silver tier is where the architecture's central insight lives: <strong style="color:var(--text)">LLMs
          generate deterministic calculation code; the calculation itself is performed and verified by deterministic
          and ML systems, not by LLMs</strong>. This is what makes the platform safe for regulated NAV production.
        </p>
        <div class="agents-row">
          <div class="agent llm"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A3 · Builder Primary</span><span class="type">LLM (Sonnet/Opus)</span></div>
          <div class="agent llm"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A3b · Builder Secondary</span><span class="type">LLM (different family)</span></div>
          <div class="agent det"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A4 · Constitution</span><span class="type">Deterministic + Z3</span></div>
          <div class="agent ml"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A5 · Anomaly</span><span class="type">Isolation Forest + EWMA</span></div>
          <div class="agent llm"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A6 · Auditor</span><span class="type">LLM (Inverse)</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="layer gold">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <div class="layer-title">Gold · Audited Posting</div>
          <span class="layer-tag">Review · Approve · Post</span>
        </div>
        <p class="layer-desc">
          The Gold tier is where humans and the production ledger live. Approved calculations enter the Tool Library
          and become reusable assets at near-zero marginal cost. This is the layer where the flywheel compounds.
        </p>
        <div class="agents-row">
          <div class="agent human"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A7 · Human Gate</span><span class="type">Reviewer</span></div>
          <div class="agent det"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A8 · Posting</span><span class="type">Deterministic ledger write</span></div>
          <div class="agent det"><span class="marker"></span><span class="name">A9 · Tool Library</span><span class="type">Precedent store</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

